## Nutrition Protocols (70kg)

**Fuel sources:**
- Gels: Roctane Ultra Endurance (sea salt chocolate) — ~25g carbs (maltodextrin/glucose), 35mg caffeine, 125mg sodium per gel
- Drink mix: carb drink with fructose in race vest flask (Maurten 320, SiS Beta Fuel, or Precision Fuel PF 90) — provides the fructose side for dual-transport absorption
- Electrolyte caps: balanced sodium + potassium + magnesium (SaltStick Caps or similar) — 1 cap delivers ~215mg sodium, ~63mg potassium, ~22mg magnesium

**Why dual-transport:** gut absorbs max ~60g/hr glucose via SGLT1. Adding fructose (separate GLUT5 transporter) allows 80-90g/hr total without GI distress. Gels provide glucose, drink mix provides fructose. Train the gut progressively from Protocol B onward.

**Protocol A — Pre + After** (sessions 75-95 min, moderate-high intensity)
- Before (90-120 min pre): 40-50g HBCDs in 500ml water
- After: 1 electrolyte cap + 5g L-glutamine in water

**Protocol B — Pre + During + After** (HIIT 75+ min, long runs 90-120 min)
- Before (90-120 min pre): 40-50g HBCDs in 500ml water + 2-3 rice cakes with Nutella, OR + ~50-60g cream of rice dry weight
- During: 1 Roctane gel midway + sip carb drink mix throughout — aim for 50-60g carbs/hr (gut training dose)
- Electrolytes: 1 cap per 45-60 min
- After: 1 electrolyte cap + 5g L-glutamine in water

**Protocol C — Pre + During + After** (long runs 120+ min, OCR simulations, race rehearsals)
- Before (90-120 min pre): 50-60g HBCDs in 500ml water + ~80-100g cream of rice dry weight with banana, OR + 3-4 rice cakes with Nutella + banana
- During: 1 Roctane gel every 25-30 min + sip carb drink mix (500ml flask, mixed strong) between gels — aim for 70-80g carbs/hr (building toward race target)
- Electrolytes: 1 cap every 30-40 min
- After: 1 electrolyte cap + 5g L-glutamine in water
- **Gut training note:** increase intake by ~10g/hr each Saturday rehearsal — Week 5 start at 60g/hr, Week 6 at 70g/hr, Week 7 at 75-80g/hr, Week 8 at 80-85g/hr

**Race Day Protocol** (3-hour effort)
- Before (2-3 hours pre): 3g/kg = ~210g carbs — 50-60g HBCDs in 500ml water + ~120-130g cream of rice dry weight with banana + Nutella, OR + 4-5 rice cakes with Nutella + banana + a few dates
- 30 min pre: 1 Roctane gel + sip water
- During: 1 Roctane gel every 20-25 min from 20 min in + sip carb drink mix (500ml flask, refill at water station if possible) — aim for 80-90g carbs/hr via dual transport
- Electrolytes: 1 cap every 25-30 min throughout
- Immediately after: 1-2 electrolyte caps + 5g L-glutamine in water
